ygData.messageBody:
No idea about the lvl of captain and cube. May be around 25 ?
Anyway, since we are on the same server, give me a tell if we are both
around the zone, and I will try to pull them to zone. I did it several times
for other fellow monks while I was camping that #@$@%!^#%&$%# alchemist in
the gorge. They are pretty common spawns, so we can be lucky.

Tsin Suchiko
42nd rank, Tunare.


-----Original Message-----
From: RaceFace [mailto:bean@...]
Sent: Thursday, February 17, 2000 11:42 AM
To: EQ-Monks@onelist.com
Subject: Re: RE: [EQ-Monks] That darn goblin alchemist.


From: "RaceFace" <bean@...>

I'm remembering back when I was a young'un many months ago, that I did see
the alchemist spawn inside the tent at the camp right by RunnyEye. I could
be wrong, but I honestly remember it spawning there. I'll camp the other
tent now, though. :)

As for the gelatinous cube and goblin captain in Runny, what level are they?
I know approximately where to find them, but have no idea what level they
are. Some friends owe me a favor for helping them camp things for their
quests, so I'm gonna call in the favor. :)

-Raean Bloodyhands, very sleepy 26th circle monk, Tunare.
